These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, mystery
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, november
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, coral
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy
2 different games are played: chess, whist
House: cottage, palace
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing chess##1
3. the person watching satire movies is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Movie-Genre      | satire   | mystery        |
| Birthday          | november    | october     |
| Color         | coral | purple   |
| Flower           | poppy  | daisy |
| Game   | chess   | whist       |
| House           | palace   | cottage      |

