.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, july
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, tram
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, sports
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, cain
City: paris, venice
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the tram is the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Birthday      | september       | july      |
| Transport          | taxi   | tram |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | sports  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey        | golf     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo       | cain   |
| City           | paris        | venice |

