2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
5. the palace house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| House      | modern      | palace   |
